    <JadeMethod name="clearFormControls" id="7df25802-e0a7-4eb0-b8f4-3568a7c0a8bc">
        <source>clearFormControls();
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date			Who		Reason
19 March 2024	navlw1	ChangeRequest 62959: CUX FR | Tk 62917 - EDBIC Make Customs references editable

